ing: 1 (16 ounce) package fresh strawberries, hulled and quartered
1 (8 ounce) package feta cheese, cut into squares
n: Spinach and Strawberry Salad with Feta Cheese
des: "Besides the variations on the dressing, I added feta cheese to the salad. It was scrumptious! Even spinach haters ate it up! I made this for a party and there were a lot more servings as a buffet item than 8."
ins:
Toss strawberries, spinach, and feta cheese together in a large bowl.
Whisk olive oil, brown sugar, white balsamic vinegar, sesame seeds, poppy seeds, and paprika together in a bowl; drizzle over salad and toss to coat.
